":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e2236c24ddbe494e0acbaf3e3531c8a496d8bf","tid":704361,"uid":48490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"鞭屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《時代》雜誌表示，每年都會選出25位最具影響力的網絡人物，並透過評估有關人物在社交媒體所產生的全球影響，以及對推動新聞的整體能力來決定入選名單。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》形容香港示威者在這場保衛香港自由的運動「沒有領袖、沒有大台」，但示威者透過網上平台，善用網上討論區「連登」和加密通訊軟件Telegram來組織向外國駐港領事館請願，以及包圍警總等行動。"},{"pid":"de58dd286b3a7158ef2a7e10daff02fdd1188a7d","tid":704361,"uid":71997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"𨳒吓都開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}